* build_vectors_regression.dts
* Build-vector runtime report proof (AIF-044 M4/M5).
*
* Runs the BUILDVECTORS command and shows the compiled capacity authority. This is the
* runtime half of GATE #1: the engine must report areas=512 (not the old inert 256) and
* the preserved fields=256 / rows=9223372036854775807. Read-only; opens/mutates nothing.
*
* Expected (grep between BEGIN/END):
*   Maximum work areas      512
*   Maximum fields          256
*   Maximum rows            9223372036854775807
*   Fingerprint             <8 hex chars>
*
* Run:  REGRESSION RUN BUILD_VECTORS
*   or: DOTSCRIPT dottalkpp/data/scripts/dotscript/build_vectors_regression.dts

SET ECHO OFF
STOP_ON_ERROR OFF

FORMULA "BUILD-VECTORS-REGRESSION-BEGIN"
FORMULA "expect areas=512 fields=256 rows=9223372036854775807 (GATE #1):"
BUILDVECTORS
FORMULA "BUILD-VECTORS-REGRESSION-END"
